# ===== Large/binary CAD or media files =====
# CAD and STL files belong in Google Drive, not this repo — Git handles
# text/code well but not binary CAD diffs. If something CAD-related ends
# up here by accident, these patterns catch the common export formats.
*.stl
*.3mf
*.step
*.stp
*.f3d
